skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: random baby name
des: This skill suggests a baby name for a girl or boy. Usage is fairly straightforward - just ask Alexa to recommend a baby name for a girl or for a boy, and it will select a name from the top 200 baby names for each gender from 2015.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
